      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 98.</p><p>Tier III: Runeblood</p><p>Prerequisite: Greater Runes</p><p>World Rune. You gain access to two additional Greater Runic Boons from your Greater Runes heroic perk, for a total of 5.</p><p>Limited Magic Immunity. You cannot be affected or detected by spells and magical effects of 7th-level or lower unless you wish to be.</p><p>Path Connections Unbreakable. Instead of the Greater Runes Heroic Perk, you can take the Stone Body Perk, changing to the Unbreakable path.</p></div>",
